{"tid":1464471,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果再買物資去機場 可以買喉糖","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:06:22.000Z","uid":109976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"42caa5f86c128b5fb5c4a2f3fa4a5110ddf747a7","tid":1464471,"uid":109976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:04:39.000Z","msg":"今日係機場企咗差唔多6個鐘 叫咗4個鐘 聽到身邊有幾位兄弟都叫到喉都沙曬<br />\n其間有人比過喉糖我 雖然食咗都係沙 但係會舒服啲嘅 多謝比糖我個位巴絲<br />\n由去到機場 到我走 全場都充滿住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Stand with Hong Kong, Fight for Freedom</span></span>嘅口號<br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無停過咁滯!!!</span></span><br />\n超級Respect<br />\n<br />\n我都只係叫咗4個鐘 比我耐嘅一定更多 所以喉糖都唔錯 我都買定幾包袋住聽日用<br />\n各位聽日機場見<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"b4c893fc1320b1784039b1ab8c52e01d9589f4bf","tid":1464471,"uid":294974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:06:22.000Z","msg":"可以入去俾下意見<br />\n===============<br />\n入機場手足可以睇睇，如果覺得講得啱，唔該幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"}]}